{"tid":2478032,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得龍門個核心問題係QC做得唔好","createTime":"2021-04-06T17:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T03:04:23.000Z","uid":123401,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3d70f59af3cc71714bab09dc087981362b366301","tid":2478032,"uid":123401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"正常茶餐廳黎講，相同野食應該幾時都係同一個味<br />\n<br />\n平時幫襯龍門都係食開咕嚕雞煲。<br />\n<br />\n但係次次去荃灣店又好，尖沙咀店又好。味道有時好酸（酸到攻鼻），有時又偏甜。雞肉都係。有時炸到勁柴勁乾，有時d酥炸左既雞皮竟然會浸到淋曬先上<br />\n<br />\n當然有時都好高質，新鮮滾熱辣。但都係睇個次好唔好彩。<br />\n<br />\n唔知係廚房佬玩野定係老細唔知呢d情況。野食既質素食多左先知咁飄忽<br />\n（唔怪得會有人屌話難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果計今日荃灣鋪lastday既質素可能我試一次都唔會再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋請既侍應，好似係人都請咁。<br />\n個觀感對比起時代真係爭好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計野食既價錢，近排海鮮餐牌，同埋限聚令下既社交距離做生意黎講，時代應該點睇都蝕得多過龍門。龍門更唔應該去到要執笠既景況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望老細可以做好QC 把關，吸取教訓<br />\n等荃灣鋪黎緊捲土重來"},{"pid":"cdec516b3f2c886a977737de90cd141dca21d9aa","tid":2478032,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVmyt1JehkmqYHGcPF8WMxPvDe1gUzYKUnD7BKDTURGqw?filename=5rLG5yo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rLG5yo.png&h=ccf52728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eddd41b1b82a26f5fb14d38669afe923e674497","tid":2478032,"uid":251696,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:54:27.000Z","msg":"知唔知咕嚕雞係咩嚟?<br />\n整煲都夠膽死出<br />\n以我多年經驗<br />\n肯撚定係強國野嚟"},{"pid":"426e15be685dd6cb1346f1222283d79f4e824fad","tid":2478032,"uid":355867,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2